Harvest 2021 has begun on the estate and to celebrate we’ve put together a lineup of SCRIBE Estate Chardonnay, Estate Pinot Noir, St. Laurent, and a back-vintage cellar selection of Skin Fermented Chardonnay.

We picked verdant basil from the farm and used garlic that has been drying in the Hacienda cellar to make fresh Pesto Genovese with a mortar and pestle. We'll include wine tasting notes and the recipe with this pack.

Link in bio. Free shipping on this Hacienda lineup !

2020 Estate Chardonnay
2017 Skin Fermented Chardonnay *Library Selection*
2018 Estate Pinot Noir
2020 St. Laurent
